Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:25.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Wait Wait, what do you want from me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.84,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}この声を聞いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:32.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Ray Ray, bringing me back to life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}誇れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.37,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}Drifting like a flawless ray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:21.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一次成形的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:23.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}已无法再倒带
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}被赋予的人生脚本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.80,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}让其大放异彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:47.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}感到些许迷茫  I leave it I leave it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:48.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}尽管看似玩世不恭
Comment: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:50.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}only one heart
